OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny daytime
OL,6,Fshowers will gradually ease for most
OL,7,Fwith perhaps the odd isolated shower
OL,8,Faffecting Kent. Otherwise, generally
OL,9,Fdry with prolonged clear spells. Winds
OL,10,Feasing, and turning locally chilly,
OL,11,Fwith a patchy frost forming in prone
OL,12,Frural spots.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FAfter a bright and chilly
OL,15,Fstart, the clouds will begin to bubble
OL,16,Fup to give sunny spells and showers,
OL,17,Flocally heavy, into the afternoon.
OL,18,FLight winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
