OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells Tuesday, after
OL,7,Fanother chilly start. Perhaps dry and
OL,8,Fbright Wednesday, before outbreaks of
OL,9,Frain arrive, clearing overnight. Sunny
OL,10,Fspells and isolated showers Thursday.
OL,11,FTemperatures above normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
